item.title: Want make new custom rsps
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

wampzzz:

ok now i need client and cache download what i need use for makeing custom server?

Typically the download should come with both the client, and server.
If they didn’t come with a cache, you should check the client to see if it’s set to automatically download it. (Ex: Look for a “CacheDownloader.java” file, I hope you can guess what that does)

@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“wampzzz, post:5, topic:554282”]yeah but i cant find server where is like cysrex brown god torvas.

pokemon minigame …[/quote]
That may be because there isn’t any released.

A big part of RSPS is making it.
Those servers never came with all those custom models (That is why they are called “customs”).
What you do is find one with content you like, and whatever content that it’s missing that you would like to add… You add it
